  "projectName": "designlang",
  "projectDescription": "A CLI tool that reverse-engineers any website's complete design system — colors, typography, spacing, shadows, and more — and outputs 8 ready-to-use files including W3C design tokens, Tailwind config, and AI-optimized markdown.",
